  "description": "This resource pack makes the Sword , Axe , Pickaxe and Shovel smaller.",
  "body": "🔧 Small Tools Pack\nThis resource pack combines the best of all my mini-sized tool textures—Small Swords, Small Pickaxes, and Small Axes—into one clean, lightweight bundle. Perfect for PvP or anyone who prefers a less cluttered screen, each tool is carefully downsized to give you more visibility without losing that vanilla Minecraft feel.\n\n✅ Features:\n\n✔️ Smaller tools models for every tier (wood, stone, iron, gold, diamond, netherite)\n\n✔️ Compact sword , pickaxe and axe textures for all materials\n\n✔️ Faithful to the vanilla Minecraft art style\n\n✔️ Ideal for PvP, survival, or aesthetic gameplay\n\n📦 Compatibility:\n\nMinecraft Java Edition\n\nNo mods required",
